Put the creditcard in the plate on the table.

Go back the same direction you came from, but continue all the way across the room until you reach a plate of drawers.
Put the credit card in the plate on the chest of drawers.
Pick up the plate from the chest of drawers.
Move to the right side of the drawer chest.
Place the plate inside the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put the Plate with the CreditCard in it inside the Drawer.

high_descs: Turn left to go straight to reach the stoveburner.
Pick the creditcard from the oven.
Turn right go straight to reach the plate.
Put the creditcard into the plate kept on the table.
Collect the plate along with the credit card.
Turn right and walk back and head to the drawer.
Put the plate in the drawer along with the credit card.
anns.task_desc: Put the Plate along with the CreditCard Drawer.
